Package butterknife

Class Summary
ButterKnife View injection utilities.
 

Enum Summary
ButterKnife.Finder A means of finding a view in either an Activity or a View.
 

Exception Summary
ButterKnife.UnableToInjectException  
ButterKnife.UnableToResetException  
 

Annotation Types Summary
InjectView Annotation for fields which indicate that it should be looked up in the view or activity layout.
OnCheckedChanged Annotation for methods which indicate that they should be called when a view is checked or unchecked.
OnClick Annotation for methods which indicate that they should be called when a view is clicked.
OnEditorAction Annotation for methods which indicate that they should be called when an edit action occurs.
OnFocusChanged Annotation for methods which indicate that they should be called when a view's focus changed.
OnItemClick Annotation for methods which indicate that they should be called when an item is clicked.
OnItemLongClick Annotation for methods which indicate that they should be called when an item is long pressed.
OnLongClick Annotation for methods which indicate that they should be called when a view is long pressed.
Optional Denote that the view specified by the injection is not required to be present.
